 E[s^X \mid \Lambda] = \sum_{n=0}^\infty \frac{(s\Lambda)^n}{n!}e^{-\Lambda} = e^{\Lambda (s-1)}. 
G_X(s) = E[s^X] = E\left[E[s^X\mid \Lambda]\right].
